                  <div class="inner section--padded"> 
                    <h2 class="section__title">Operating for over 15 years</h2>

                    <p>CarSafeKids is a Melbourne based accredited company who specialise in the expert fitting of child restraints. With over fifteen years of professional experience in the industry, CarSafeKids adheres to the following principals:</p>

                    <table>
                      <tbody>
                        <tr>
                          <td>Choice</td> 
                          <td>Knowing what to buy for your child is IMPERATIVE</td> 
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                          <td>Installation</td> 
                          <td>Knowing your restraint is fitted correctly is CRUCIAL</td> 
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                          <td>Education</td> 
                          <td>Knowing how to use your restraint is ESSENTIAL</td> 
                        </tr>
                      </tbody>
                    </table>

                    <p>CarSafeKids offers a premium fitting service whilst also offering obligation free advice pertaining purchase & consultation, installation, education and general advice. We pride ourselves in providing a service that is honest, courteous and punctual. <br/>CarSafeKids - <em>Keeping kids safe!</em></p>

                    <a class="button" href="#" title="Read more about Pete">Read more about Pete</a>
